### Member API 시나리오

### 변수 설정
@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080/api
@contentType = application/json

### 1. 회원가입
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/v1/signup
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "email": "test@test.com",
  "password": "test1234",
  "displayName": "Test User"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("username", response.body.username);
%}

### 2. 로그인
POST {{baseUrl}}/members/v1/login
Content-Type: {{contentType}}

{
  "username": "testuser",
  "password": "test1234"
}

> {%
  client.global.set("accessToken", response.body.accessToken);
%}

### 3. 회원 정보 조회
GET {{baseUrl}}/members/v1/{{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

### 4. 회원 정보 수정
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/members/v1/{{username}}
Content-Type: {{contentType}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}

{
  "displayName": "Updated User"
}

### 5. 회원 탈퇴
DELETE {{baseUrl}}/members/v1/{{username}}
Authorization: Bearer {{accessToken}}
